dk.itu.jesl.hash

Class TabHasher

  • java.lang.Object
    • dk.itu.jesl.hash.TabHasher

  • public final class TabHasher
extends java.lang.Object
    Support for tabular hash functions. This class does not implement Hasher, but rather is used to create one. It contains methods to create Hasher.Factorys for some fixed key classes.

    • Nested Class Summary

      An interface for which (among other alternatives) a TabHasher can compute hash values.
